# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# .ignore — Ripgrep exceptions
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# This file tells ripgrep (rg) to search directories that are
# in .gitignore. Does NOT affect git — only rg/grep tools.
#
# See: https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep/blob/master/GUIDE.md#automatic-filtering
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# AI agent instructions and skills (useful for searching conventions)
!.agents/
!.agent/
!.qwen/

# SDD artifacts (proposals, specs, designs)
!.atl/
